						<summary>

						<p>States that a certain <hi rend="bold">Dāmanāmātya</hi> of Lōhita-<hi rend="italic">gōtra</hi> consecrated the image of god Sūrēśvara, built a temple and <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> for the same and also endowed it with land for the merit of <hi rend="bold">Leṅkavaṇṭi Kōka,</hi> the minister of <hi rend="bold">Kākatīya Gaṇapatidēva</hi> and of a certain <hi rend="bold">Annaya.</hi></p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

